<https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/vocabulary#redefinedFeature> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Redefinition: The Feature that is redefined by the redefiningFeature of this Redefinition." .
<https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/vocabulary#redefinedFeature> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://www.omg.org/spec/kerml/vocabulary#> .
